text: Jean-Charles Valladont is an archer from France. He was born on 20 March 1989. Valladont competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics, 2016 Summer Olympics, and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Jean-Charles VALLADONTJean-Charles Valladont == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:French archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for France Category:Sportspeople from Besan√ßon
